Our Vision: KHOJ (Search)

KHOJ, meaning "search," simplifies reconnecting lost items with their rightful owners. We aim to provide a centralized and accessible platform for lost and found belongings.

Our goal is to foster peace of mind by building a supportive community that helps return lost items to where they belong — quickly and securely.
